    "title": "Teeth Retainer: How It Works & How Much It Costs",
    "article": "\n<p>Teeth retainers are like braces, but for after braces. They keep your teeth straight after braces are taken off. Without retainers, teeth can move back to their old spots, which undoes all the work braces did. We've listed five essential things you need to know about teeth retainers.</p>\n<img alt=\"Teeth Retainer: How It Works &amp; How Much It Costs_1\" class=\"old_img\" data-smallsrc=\"//cdn.uslowcostdental.com/Images/content_small/teeth-retainer-how-it-works-and-how-much-it-costs/teeth-retainer-how-it-works-and-how-much-it-costs_1.jpg\" data-src=\"//cdn.uslowcostdental.com/Images/content/teeth-retainer-how-it-works-and-how-much-it-costs/teeth-retainer-how-it-works-and-how-much-it-costs_1.jpg\" data-webpsmallsrc=\"//cdn.uslowcostdental.com/Images/content_small/teeth-retainer-how-it-works-and-how-much-it-costs/teeth-retainer-how-it-works-and-how-much-it-costs_1.webp\" data-webpsrc=\"//cdn.uslowcostdental.com/Images/content/teeth-retainer-how-it-works-and-how-much-it-costs/teeth-retainer-how-it-works-and-how-much-it-costs_1.webp\" lazyload=\"\" src=\"/Public/Images/load.png\">\n</img>"
  },
  {
    "page": 2,
    "title": "Teeth Retainer: How It Works & How Much It Costs",
    "article": "\n<h4>1. What Is A Teeth Retainer?</h4>\n<img alt=\"Teeth Retainer: How It Works &amp; How Much It Costs_2\" class=\"old_img\" data-smallsrc=\"//cdn.uslowcostdental.com/Images/content_small/teeth-retainer-how-it-works-and-how-much-it-costs/teeth-retainer-how-it-works-and-how-much-it-costs_2.jpg\" data-src=\"//cdn.uslowcostdental.com/Images/content/teeth-retainer-how-it-works-and-how-much-it-costs/teeth-retainer-how-it-works-and-how-much-it-costs_2.jpg\" data-webpsmallsrc=\"//cdn.uslowcostdental.com/Images/content_small/teeth-retainer-how-it-works-and-how-much-it-costs/teeth-retainer-how-it-works-and-how-much-it-costs_2.webp\" data-webpsrc=\"//cdn.uslowcostdental.com/Images/content/teeth-retainer-how-it-works-and-how-much-it-costs/teeth-retainer-how-it-works-and-how-much-it-costs_2.webp\" lazyload=\"\" src=\"/Public/Images/load.png\">\n<p>A teeth retainer is a custom-made device for the mouth made of wire and plastic. It helps keep teeth in place after braces. The retainer stops your teeth from moving back, and can be taken out or fixed inside the mouth. They are worn for some time each day or night.</p>\n</img>"
  },
  {
    "page": 3,
    "title": "Teeth Retainer: How It Works & How Much It Costs",
    "article": "\n<h4>2. How Much Do Teeth Retainers Cost?</h4>\n<img alt=\"Teeth Retainer: How It Works &amp; How Much It Costs_3\" class=\"old_img\" data-smallsrc=\"//cdn.uslowcostdental.com/Images/content_small/teeth-retainer-how-it-works-and-how-much-it-costs/teeth-retainer-how-it-works-and-how-much-it-costs_3.jpg\" data-src=\"//cdn.uslowcostdental.com/Images/content/teeth-retainer-how-it-works-and-how-much-it-costs/teeth-retainer-how-it-works-and-how-much-it-costs_3.jpg\" data-webpsmallsrc=\"//cdn.uslowcostdental.com/Images/content_small/teeth-retainer-how-it-works-and-how-much-it-costs/teeth-retainer-how-it-works-and-how-much-it-costs_3.webp\" data-webpsrc=\"//cdn.uslowcostdental.com/Images/content/teeth-retainer-how-it-works-and-how-much-it-costs/teeth-retainer-how-it-works-and-how-much-it-costs_3.webp\" lazyload=\"\" src=\"/Public/Images/load.png\">\n<p>The price of teeth retainers can change based on the kind your orthodontist suggests. A wire retainer usually costs $150 to $500, while an Invisalign retainer can be $500 to $1500. Talk to your orthodontist about this cost to decide which option fits your budget best. </p>\n</img>"
  },
  {
    "page": 4,
    "title": "Teeth Retainer: How It Works & How Much It Costs",
    "article": "\n<h4>3. How Long To Wear A Teeth Retainer?</h4>\n<img alt=\"Teeth Retainer: How It Works &amp; How Much It Costs_4\" class=\"old_img\" data-smallsrc=\"//cdn.uslowcostdental.com/Images/content_small/teeth-retainer-how-it-works-and-how-much-it-costs/teeth-retainer-how-it-works-and-how-much-it-costs_4.jpg\" data-src=\"//cdn.uslowcostdental.com/Images/content/teeth-retainer-how-it-works-and-how-much-it-costs/teeth-retainer-how-it-works-and-how-much-it-costs_4.jpg\" data-webpsmallsrc=\"//cdn.uslowcostdental.com/Images/content_small/teeth-retainer-how-it-works-and-how-much-it-costs/teeth-retainer-how-it-works-and-how-much-it-costs_4.webp\" data-webpsrc=\"//cdn.uslowcostdental.com/Images/content/teeth-retainer-how-it-works-and-how-much-it-costs/teeth-retainer-how-it-works-and-how-much-it-costs_4.webp\" lazyload=\"\" src=\"/Public/Images/load.png\">\n<p>The time you wear teeth retainers can differ based on your orthodontist's advice. Normally, you wear retainers all the time (during the day and night) for a few months after removing braces. Later on, the orthodontist might suggest wearing them only at night to keep the results from braces.</p>\n</img>"
  },
  {
    "page": 5,
    "title": "Teeth Retainer: How It Works & How Much It Costs",
    "article": "\n<h4>4. How Do Teeth Retainers Work?</h4>\n<img alt=\"Teeth Retainer: How It Works &amp; How Much It Costs_5\" class=\"old_img\" data-smallsrc=\"//cdn.uslowcostdental.com/Images/content_small/teeth-retainer-how-it-works-and-how-much-it-costs/teeth-retainer-how-it-works-and-how-much-it-costs_5.jpg\" data-src=\"//cdn.uslowcostdental.com/Images/content/teeth-retainer-how-it-works-and-how-much-it-costs/teeth-retainer-how-it-works-and-how-much-it-costs_5.jpg\" data-webpsmallsrc=\"//cdn.uslowcostdental.com/Images/content_small/teeth-retainer-how-it-works-and-how-much-it-costs/teeth-retainer-how-it-works-and-how-much-it-costs_5.webp\" data-webpsrc=\"//cdn.uslowcostdental.com/Images/content/teeth-retainer-how-it-works-and-how-much-it-costs/teeth-retainer-how-it-works-and-how-much-it-costs_5.webp\" lazyload=\"\" src=\"/Public/Images/load.png\">\n<p>Teeth retainers keep your teeth in place by using gentle pressure. They stop your teeth from moving and help them stay straight. Retainers are made just for you and should feel comfortable when you wear them.</p>\n</img>"
  },
  {
    "page": 6,
    "title": "Teeth Retainer: How It Works & How Much It Costs",
    "article": "\n<h4>5. How Long Does It Take For Your Retainers To Fix Your Teeth?</h4>\n<img alt=\"Teeth Retainer: How It Works &amp; How Much It Costs_6\" class=\"old_img\" data-smallsrc=\"//cdn.uslowcostdental.com/Images/content_small/teeth-retainer-how-it-works-and-how-much-it-costs/teeth-retainer-how-it-works-and-how-much-it-costs_6.jpg\" data-src=\"//cdn.uslowcostdental.com/Images/content/teeth-retainer-how-it-works-and-how-much-it-costs/teeth-retainer-how-it-works-and-how-much-it-costs_6.jpg\" data-webpsmallsrc=\"//cdn.uslowcostdental.com/Images/content_small/teeth-retainer-how-it-works-and-how-much-it-costs/teeth-retainer-how-it-works-and-how-much-it-costs_6.webp\" data-webpsrc=\"//cdn.uslowcostdental.com/Images/content/teeth-retainer-how-it-works-and-how-much-it-costs/teeth-retainer-how-it-works-and-how-much-it-costs_6.webp\" lazyload=\"\" src=\"/Public/Images/load.png\">\n<p>The time it takes to wear teeth retainers can be different for everyone. Normally, you need to  wear retainers for about a year after getting braces off. But some may need to wear them longer to keep their teeth straight.</p>\n</img>"
  }
